sys_hub_flow.description:
This flow is designed to retrieve ERP number data from the SAP ECC RFC system.

Inputs:

  • PSM Goods Receipt - Referece record to receipt record.
  • Connection Name - This input is a Connection and Credential alias record used to connect to the target system.

Outputs:

  • Status - Will be set to "Success", if the request is "Success" or will be set to "Error", if the request is "Error”.
  • Error - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.

To use this subflow, the corresponding SAP ECC RFC connection and credential must be created and associated with the SAP ECC RFC Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.

sys_hub_flow_snapshot.description:
This flow is designed to retrieve ERP number data from the SAP ECC RFC system.

Inputs:

  • PSM Goods Receipt - Referece record to receipt record.
  • Connection Name - This input is a Connection and Credential alias record used to connect to the target system.

Outputs:

  • Status - Will be set to "Success", if the request is "Success" or will be set to "Error", if the request is "Error”.
  • Error - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.

To use this subflow, the corresponding SAP ECC RFC connection and credential must be created and associated with the SAP ECC RFC Connection & Credential alias. Learn More

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More.
